.TH LOCALE-TESTER 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "Locale Tester Manual"
.SH NAME
locale-tester - Test and compare locale settings
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B locale-tester
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBlocale-tester\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for inspecting and comparing system locale settings on Linux. It displays dates, time, numbers, currency, percent, collation order, weekday and month names, decimal and thousands separators, allows side-by-side locale comparison, includes a strftime tester, and shows LC_* environment variable overview.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/locale-tester/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/locale-tester/
Cached data.
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at https://github.com/yeager/locale-tester/issues
